title: Who Are the Most Intriguing Free Agents and Trade Targets? | Group Chat
description:
Justin, Rob, and Wos start by discussing the trade between the Denver Nuggets and Washington Wizards and what the Nuggets could look like with their new additions. Then they each discuss one restricted and one unrestricted free agent that intrigues them (7:12). Then they each talk about some of the most interesting trade targets (51:27).

Hosts: Justin Verrier, Rob Mahoney, Wosny Lambre
Associate Producer: Isaiah Blakely
Additional Production Supervision: Benjamin Cruz
